                                help you?
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <form id="interaction1-5" class="create-form hide">

                        <div class="form-group">

                            <p>
                                They are other spirits like myself, who were trapped here throughout time, but we want
                                to
                                leave
                                now. When I died in a BMX accident, I just couldn’t let myself leave here. And now I’m
                                stuck. Just
                                give
                                the
                                others one of these keys and get on their good side to convince them to leave the house
                                for
                                good. If
                                you
                                help
                                me, I can leave.`
                            </p>

                        </div>
                        {{!-- pos show 1.7 --}}
                        <div id="positiveBtn6">
                            <a class="button secondary" id="posBtn3" for="positive" type="submit" name="posBtn" href="/foyer/1">I
